               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1r" to="673v">1r-673v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="acephalous apodous lacunous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA">قران</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1r">-1r</locus>نبذ فريق من الذين اوتو الكا الكتاب كتاب الله وراء ظهورهم</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#673v">-673v</locus>حتى مطلع الفجر سورة البينة مدينة وهي تسع ايات بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم لم</explicit>
                     <note>The text begins with the verse 2:101 and ends with the beginning of sura 98. Fol. 486 is bound in wrong place: it should be between fols 434 and 435.  Lacuna between fols 652v and 653r. Fol. 398v is blank but no lacuna in the text. Some of the words are divided into two lines. Vocalized.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
